FBIS4-13106 "drnes074_n_94012" FBIS-NES-94-074 Daily Report 17 Apr 1994 LEBANON Junblatt Opposes Rocket Attacks on Northern Israel Junblatt Opposes Rocket Attacks on Northern Israel NC1704110794 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1030 GMT 17 Apr 94 NC1704110794 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] In an interview with the newspaper AL-HAYAH, Minister Walid Junblatt expressed his opposition to the rocket bombardment of northern Israel, describing it as politically unprofitable. Junblatt said such attacks might create conditions similar to those leading to the 1982 invasion of Lebanon.
